---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Educators — Litia">
  <h1 class="pageTitle">Educators &amp; schools</h1>
  <p class="subtle">Built for early literacy environments: clean screens, short sessions, fast feedback.</p>

  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Classroom-ready activities</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Eye-tracked quizzes for letters, phonemes, and vocabulary prompts.</li>
      <li>Read-along stories with simplified folk tales and fairy tales.</li>
      <li>Guided flashcards that pair gaze, images, and spoken language.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Family + educator settings</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Private dashboards that show detailed learning progress.</li>
      <li>Downloadable reports for lesson planning and research.</li>
      <li>Local-first data storage with secure, offline defaults.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Pilot goals (2–6 weeks)</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Get Litia into a small number of classrooms.</li>
      <li>Collect structured feedback on curriculum flow and UI.</li>
      <li>Iterate quickly with educator input.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Want a pilot? <a href={`${Astro.base}/contact`}>Request access</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
